    <p>[+++++++++++++++]</p>
    <p>The purpose of this Number Talk is to elicit strategies and understandings students have for multiplying within 100 and to help students develop fluency.</p>
<p>When students use known multiplication facts to multiply larger numbers, they look for and make use of structure (MP7).</p>
