  <!-- Síntesis de la actividad -->
  <paragraphs>
    <title><custom ref="synthesis-actividad-titulo"/></title>
    <p>[+++++++++++++++]</p>
    <ul>
      <li>
        <q>¿Cómo usaron los hechos de multiplicación que ya conocen para encontrar algunos de los otros productos?</q>  (I knew that <m>3\times10</m> is 30, so <m>3\times13</m> would be 3 groups of 10 and 3 groups of 3 which is 39. Once I knew <m>3\times13</m>, I was able to find <m>6\times13</m> by doubling 39 which is 78.)
      </li>
    </ul>
  </paragraphs>


